## Blocked on v1.0.0 (Intentionally Deferred)

These items are **explicitly out of scope** for v0.5.0:

- Smart contract mainnet deployment
- Real ETH gas handling
- External security audit
- Multi-provider RPC failover
- HashiCorp Vault integration
- OAuth2 / social login

---

## Dependency: v0.4.27

v0.5.0 **requires** v0.4.27 to be completed first:

| v0.4.27 Task | Blocks v0.5.0? |
|-------------|----------------|
| JWT migration complete | Yes — state changes need auth first |
| deps.py deleted | No — but should be done |
| ShellCheck in CI | No — independent |
| detect-secrets in CI | No — independent |
| Ruff clean | No — independent |

