## Release Checklist

Before tagging v0.5.0:

- [ ] DB/Redis state backing complete (0 module-global `dict()`)
- [ ] Systemd units hardened
- [ ] `/metrics` endpoints on all services
- [ ] Load tests run and pass
- [ ] No P0/P1 security issues in internal review

---

## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Impact | Likelihood | Mitigation |
|------|--------|-----------|------------|
| Redis dependency adds ops complexity | Medium | High | Document Redis setup, add health checks |
| Systemd hardening breaks dev workflows | Medium | Medium | Keep dev scripts working, only harden systemd units |
| Load tests reveal fundamental scaling issues | High | Low | Start load tests early in cycle, not at end |

